---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Disclaimer — xCrypto24" description="Important disclaimers about using xCrypto24. Cryptocurrency is high risk. We provide data only, not financial advice." keywords="crypto disclaimer, not financial advice, cryptocurrency risk, xcrypto24 disclaimer">
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"WebPage","name":"Disclaimer — xCrypto24","url":"https://xcrypto24.com/disclaimer","description":"Important disclaimers about using xCrypto24. Cryptocurrency is high risk. We provide data only, not financial advice."})} />
  <div style="max-width:800px;margin:2rem auto;padding:0 1rem;">
    <h1 style="font-size:2rem;font-weight:700;color:#fafafa;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Disclaimer</h1>
    <p style="color:#71717a;font-size:0.85rem;margin-bottom:2rem;">Last updated: June 2026</p>

    <div style="margin:1.5rem 0;padding:1.2rem;border-radius:12px;border:2px solid rgba(239,68,68,0.4);background:rgba(127,29,29,0.15);">
      <p style="font-size:0.8rem;font-weight:600;color:#f87171;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">⚠️ Important</p>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:#e4e4e7;line-height:1.7;">Cryptocurrency is <strong>extremely high risk</strong>. You can lose 100% of your investment. Many tokens go to zero. Past performance does not indicate future results. Never invest more than you can afford to lose entirely.</p>
    </div>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:300;color:#c084fc;margin-top:2.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem;border-left:4px solid #8b5cf6;padding-left:1rem;">Not Financial Advice</h2>
    <p style="color:#d4d4d8;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1rem;">xCrypto24 is a data aggregation tool. Nothing displayed on this website — including prices, market caps, safety scores, trend indicators, or any other metric — constitutes financial advice, investment recommendation, or solicitation to buy or sell any cryptocurrency.</p>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:300;color:#c084fc;margin-top:2.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem;border-left:4px solid #8b5cf6;padding-left:1rem;">Third-Party Data</h2>
    <p style="color:#d4d4d8;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1rem;">All price, volume, holder, and safety data comes from third-party sources (DexScreener, RugCheck.xyz, GeckoTerminal). We do not verify, audit, or guarantee the accuracy of this data. It may be delayed, incorrect, or manipulated at source.</p>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:300;color:#c084fc;margin-top:2.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem;border-left:4px solid #8b5cf6;padding-left:1rem;">Safety Scores</h2>
    <div style="margin:1rem 0;padding:1rem;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(239,68,68,0.3);background:rgba(127,29,29,0.1);">
      <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#fca5a5;line-height:1.6;">Safety scores (Safe, Caution, Risky) are algorithmic assessments from RugCheck.xyz. A "Safe" score does NOT guarantee a token is safe. A "Risky" score does NOT guarantee a rug pull will occur. These are heuristic indicators, not guarantees. Tokens can be rugged regardless of their safety score.</p>
    </div>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:300;color:#c084fc;margin-top:2.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem;border-left:4px solid #8b5cf6;padding-left:1rem;">Token Listings</h2>
    <p style="color:#d4d4d8;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1rem;">The appearance of any token on xCrypto24 does not constitute endorsement, recommendation, or verification of that token's legitimacy. Users add tokens to their own tracking lists. We do not curate, vet, or audit listed tokens.</p>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:300;color:#c084fc;margin-top:2.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem;border-left:4px solid #8b5cf6;padding-left:1rem;">Risk Acknowledgement</h2>
    <p style="color:#d4d4d8;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1rem;">By using xCrypto24, you acknowledge that:</p>
    <div style="margin:1rem 0;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:0.75rem;">
      <div style="padding:0.8rem 1rem;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #3f3f5a;background:#16161f;"><p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#d4d4d8;">Cryptocurrency markets are volatile and can result in total loss</p></div>
      <div style="padding:0.8rem 1rem;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #3f3f5a;background:#16161f;"><p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#d4d4d8;">You are solely responsible for your trading and investment decisions</p></div>
      <div style="padding:0.8rem 1rem;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #3f3f5a;background:#16161f;"><p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#d4d4d8;">Memecoins and low-cap tokens carry extreme risk of fraud and manipulation</p></div>
      <div style="padding:0.8rem 1rem;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #3f3f5a;background:#16161f;"><p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#d4d4d8;">xCrypto24 bears no liability for any losses you incur</p></div>
      <div style="padding:0.8rem 1rem;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #3f3f5a;background:#16161f;"><p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:#d4d4d8;">You should always DYOR (Do Your Own Research) before investing</p></div>
    </div>

    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:300;color:#c084fc;margin-top:2.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem;border-left:4px solid #8b5cf6;padding-left:1rem;">Regulatory Notice</h2>
    <p style="color:#d4d4d8;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1rem;">Cryptocurrency regulation varies by jurisdiction. It is your responsibility to ensure compliance with your local laws regarding cryptocurrency trading and taxation. xCrypto24 does not provide tax, legal, or regulatory advice.</p>

    <div style="margin-top:2rem;text-align:center;">
      <a href="/" style="color:#71717a;font-size:0.85rem;text-decoration:none;">← Back to home</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
